name: Daylight
tagline: Daylight  is a calendar application and appointment manager
body:
### Welcome to Daylight

Daylight is a day-planner calendar application. It uses Qt5 and SqLite3. 

At the moment, daylight is in an early development stage. Please use it on your own risk. The database schema will change and there is no functionality for backward compatibility.

Have fun.
